      Trigger : Exporter have status 0 or other of KB system {{ $labels.vhost }} HTTP error for 1m
      responsable: Andrius Kubickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Dominykas about Nexus availability and healthcheck.
  - alert: 12.2 kb_db_activity_yellow
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9105", job="kb_mysql_exporter", name="kb_exporter"} == 0
    for: 5m
    labels:
      severity: event.yellow.kb
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : KB 
      Trigger : Teampass MySQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 5 min
      responsable: Dominykas Sivickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check MYSQL docker container is running or not on FLT-MM-BS server. If FLT-MM-BS (192.168.50.54) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 12.2 kb_db_activity_orange
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9105", job="kb_mysql_exporter", name="kb_exporter"} == 0
    for: 10m
    labels:
      severity: event.orange
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : KB
      Trigger : KB MySQL db activity > 10 min
      responsable: Dominykas Sivickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action:  Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check MYSQL docker container is running or not on FLT-MM-BS server. If FLT-MM-BS (192.168.50.54) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 12.2 kb_db_activity_red
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9105", job="kb_mysql_exporter", name="kb_exporter"} == 0
    for: 15m
    labels:
      severity: event.red
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : KB
      Trigger :  KB MySQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 15 min
      responsable: Andrius Kubickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Dominykas Sivickas to check MySQL is available or not. Ask Dominykas send communication for DB's downtime .
