      responsable: Andrius Kubickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Vadimas Klepko about BI2 availability, communication
  - alert: 18.2 BI2_db_activity_yellow
    expr: mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state < 2 or absent(mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state)
    for: 5m
    labels:
      severity: event.yellow.bi2_DB
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : BI2
      Trigger : Bi2, Bi2_erp MSSQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 5 min
      responsable: Tomas Zemblys
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check BI2 database on FLTSQL server. If FLTSQL (192.168.50.10) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 18.2 BI2_db_activity_orange
    expr: mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state < 2 or absent(mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state)
    for: 15m
    labels:
      severity: event.orange
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : BI2
      Trigger : Bi2, Bi2_erp MSSQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 10 min
      responsable: Tomas Zemblys
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: n	Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check BI2 database on FLTSQL server. If FLTSQL (192.168.50.10) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 18.2 BI2_db_activity_red
    expr: mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state < 2 or absent(mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2_state)
    for: 20m
    labels:
      severity: event.red
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : BI2
      Trigger : Bi2, Bi2_erp MSSQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 15 min
      responsable: Tomas Zemblys
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Tomas Zemblys to check MSSQL is DB BI2 and BI2_erp available or not. Ask Tomas Zemblys send communication for DB's downtime.
  - alert: 18.2 BI2_kiosk_activity_yellow
    expr: mssql_entrance_KUN_HGR_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_KUN_WH_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_ADM_1a_1_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_ADM_1a_2_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_HGR_kiosk_status < 4
    for: 30m
    labels:
      severity: event.yellow.bi2
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : BI2 Kiosk
      Trigger : bi2 Kiosk status >= 0 and time >= 30 min
      responsable: Vadimas Klepko
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check if available Kiosk mentioned in the alert. If Kiosk is not available then ask SD to check Internet connection to bi2.fltechnics.com.
  - alert: 18.2 BI2_kiosk_activity_orange
    expr: mssql_entrance_KUN_HGR_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_KUN_WH_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_ADM_1a_1_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_ADM_1a_2_kiosk_status + mssql_entrance_VNO_HGR_kiosk_status < 4
    for: 40m
    labels:
      severity: event.orange
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : BI2 Kiosk
      Trigger : bi2 Kiosk status >= 0 and time >= 40 min
      responsable: Vadimas Klepko
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check if available Kiosk mentioned in the alert. If Kiosk is not available then ask SD to check Internet connection to bi2.fltechnics.com.
