  - alert: 22.2 safety_db_activity_yellow
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9106", job="safety_mysql_exporter", name="safety_exporter"} == 0
    for: 5m
    labels:
      severity: event.yellow.safety
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety 
      Trigger : Teampass MySQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 5 min
      responsable: Dominykas Sivickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check MYSQL docker container is running or not on FLT-MM-BS server. If FLT-MM-BS (192.168.50.54) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 22.2 safety_db_activity_orange
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9106", job="safety_mysql_exporter", name="safety_exporter"} == 0
    for: 10m
    labels:
      severity: event.orange
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety
      Trigger : safety MySQL db activity > 10 min
      responsable: Dominykas Sivickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action:  Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check MYSQL docker container is running or not on FLT-MM-BS server. If FLT-MM-BS (192.168.50.54) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 22.2 safety_db_activity_red
    expr: mysql_up{instance="192.168.231.235:9106", job="safety_mysql_exporter", name="safety_exporter"} == 0
    for: 15m
    labels:
      severity: event.red
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety
      Trigger :  safety MySQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 15 min
      responsable: Andrius Kubickas
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Dominykas Sivickas to check MySQL is available or not. Ask Dominykas send communication for DB's downtime .
  - alert: 22.3 safety_db_activity_DiskRunningFull_yellow
    expr: 100 - ((node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"} * 100) / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"}) > 90
    for: 10m
    labels:
      severity: event.yellow.safety
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety 
      Trigger : File system on FLT-App-Samba server on mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety" is more than 90proc
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check SMB Volume size on FLT-App-Samba server on mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"
  - alert: 22.3 safety_db_activity_DiskRunningFull_orange
    expr: 100 - ((node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"} * 100) / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"}) > 90
    for: 20m
    labels:
      severity: event.orange
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety 
      Trigger : File system on FLT-App-Samba server on mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety" is more than 90proc
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Check SMB Volume size on FLT-App-Samba server on mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"
  - alert: 22.3 safety_db_activity_DiskRunningFull_red
    expr: 100 - ((node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"} * 100) / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety"}) > 90
    for: 30m
    labels:
      severity: event.red
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : safety 
      Trigger : File system on FLT-App-Samba server on mountpoint="/home/app/share/safety" is more than 90proc
      timestamp: >
