      Action: Check if available DB mentioned in the alert. If DB is not available then start DB or restore DB. If DB available then check bi2v2 database on FLTSQL server. If FLT-SQL-DEV (192.168.50.210) VM is down ask ASG to turn on VM.
  - alert: 24.2 bi2v2_db_activity_red
    expr: mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2v2 == 0 or absent(mssql_fltsql_db_service_bi2v2)
    for: 15m
    labels:
      severity: event.red
    annotations:
      Inpacted_Service : bi2v2
      Trigger : bi2v2 MSSQL DB status >= 0 and time >= 15 min
      responsable: Tomas Zemblys
      timestamp: >
        time: {{ with query "time()" }}{{ . | first | value | humanizeTimestamp }}{{ end }}
      Action: Ask Tomas Zemblys to check FLT-SQL-DEV is DB bi2v2 available or not. Ask Tomas Zemblys send communication for DB's downtime.
